num_files_changed: How many files were modified in this commit
num_lines_changed: How many lines changed throughout all files
gunning_fog_approx: An approximation of the gunning-fog index, a measure of the legibility of English sentences
num_chars: Number of characters in the commit message
num_words: Number of words in the commit message
closes_issue: Whether or not this commit closes an open issue
rank_message_length: Subjective rank of the length of the commit message, 1-5 scale
rank_message_readability: Subject rank of legibility/readability of commit message, scale 1-5
rank_commit_size: Rank of the size of the commit (how many files/lines changed), scale 1-5
rank_commit_overall: Overall rank of the commit, with a bonus for closing an issue
